OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FOutbreaks of
OL,6,Frain, with some hill snow in the
OL,7,Fnorth, rain continuing southeastwards
OL,8,Facross the north and west of England
OL,9,Fand Wales. Dry with low cloud to the
OL,10,Fsoutheast. Clearer with frost further
OL,11,Flater for Northern Ireland and western
OL,12,FScotland.
OL,13,
OL,14,CFriday:FRain will edge southeastwards
OL,15,Facross England and Wales. Scotland and
OL,16,FNorthern Ireland look largely dry with
OL,17,Fsome sunshine, reaching Wales and the
OL,18,Fnorth and west of England later.
OL,19,FGenerally cooler.
